Package: qoobot-brain-core
Version: 1.0.0
Section: robotics
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ros-humble-ros-base, libprotobuf-dev, libgrpc++-dev, protobuf-compiler-grpc, libfcl-dev, libeigen3-dev
Maintainer: QooBot Team <dev@qoobot.dev>
Homepage: https://github.com/qoobots/qoobot
Description: QooBot Brain Core — Real-time robotics control engine
 QooBot Brain is a humanoid robot operating system module that translates
 natural language instructions into robot execution.
 .
 This package provides the C++17 real-time control engine including:
  - ROS 2 Humble nodes for robot hardware abstraction
  - Behavior tree execution engine (BehaviorTree.CPP 4.x)
  - Motion planning with MoveIt 2 + TRAC-IK + STOMP
  - Safety monitoring (S0-S3 alert levels)
  - Event bus for cross-component communication
  - gRPC server for AI engine integration
 .
 Target hardware: Jetson Orin + Kinova Gen3 arm + TurtleBot 4
